<td><i>Desiderantes meliorem patriam</i></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Eligibility</th>
<td>All living Canadians, except federal and provincial politicians and judges while holding office.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Awarded for</th>
